************************************************************
You'll need to configure
	/usr/local/etc/nntpcache/nntpcache.access
	/usr/local/etc/nntpcache/nntpcache.config
	/usr/local/etc/nntpcache/nntpcache.servers
from distributed samples, and create
	/usr/local/etc/rc.d/nntpcached.sh
to activate nntpcache.

NOTE: This software is NOT free.  Be sure to read the file
/usr/local/share/doc/nntpcache/LICENSING for details.
************************************************************
